From d4340c9e529027f05a8cf15e6fb51ea402e8ae94 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Arun Raghavan <arunr@valvesoftware.com>
Date: Wed, 11 Feb 2026 15:06:56 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 11/18] spa: alsa: Add a mechanism for external volume control

Currently enabled at device creation and delegated to an external entity
via a varlink protocol.
---
 spa/plugins/alsa/acp/acp.c         | 337 +++++++++++++++++------
 spa/plugins/alsa/acp/acp.h         |   9 +
 spa/plugins/alsa/acp/card.h        |   2 +
